	<div style="background:#f3f3f3;color:#565656;font-family:Avenir,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:100;padding:40px 20px;text-align:center" align="center">
	    <div style="margin:40px auto;font-size: 20px"><p>Need any help? we love to support you, please write to us at <a href="#" target="_blank" style="color:#185285;font-weight:bold" target="_blank">theofficecapital.com</a>.</p>
